  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to better understand how a daytime nap after training&#xD;
      on a motor skill after brain injury improves performance compared with the same amount of&#xD;
      time after training spent awake and resting.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
